title US2.2.2 â€“ Register and Update Vessel Records (SSD)

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
boundary "Vessel Management API" as System

== Register (Create Vessel) ==
Officer -> System : POST /api/vessel\nBody: { imoNumber, name, owner, vesselTypeId }
System --> Officer : 201 Created\nBody: VesselDto

== Update (Partial Edit) ==
Officer -> System : PATCH /api/vessel/imo/{imo}\nBody: { name?, owner? }
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: VesselDto (updated)

== Search (Read Vessel Information) ==
Officer -> System : GET /api/vessel/imo/{imo}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: VesselDto

Officer -> System : GET /api/vessel/name/{name}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: List<VesselDto>

Officer -> System : GET /api/vessel/owner/{owner}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: List<VesselDto>

Officer -> System : GET /api/vessel/filter?name=&imo=&owner=&query=
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: List<VesselDto>
@enduml
